Courses collection has:
An info Document for each course. (e.g. course title, Modules numbers, visibility.. etc)


Every course has:
Two collections for each module
a collection of module headers ($CourseName$ModuleNumberHeaders) e.g. A1Module1Headers
has one info Document (0-index) and many scene headers Documents.  

a collection of module scenes ($CourseName$ModuleNumberScenes) e.g. A1Module1Scenes
has many scene Documents.

